text: Chiang Wing Hung (born 11 January 1962) is a Hong Kong rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Hong Kong male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hong Kong Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in rowing Category:Rowers at the 1994 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Hong Kong Category:Medalists at the 1994 Asian Games
